$$
\begin{bmatrix}
M + \frac{3}{2}mL &amp; \frac{3}{4}ML \\
\frac{3}{4}ML &amp; \frac{9L^2}{32}(mL + 2M)
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot{y} \\
\ddot{\theta}
\end{bmatrix}+
\begin{bmatrix}
k_1 + k_2 &amp; \frac{1}{4}(k_2 - 3k_1)L \\
\frac{1}{4}(k_2 - 3k_1)L &amp; \frac{1}{16}(9k_1 + k_2)L^2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
y \\
\theta
\end{bmatrix}=
\begin{bmatrix}
-Mg - \frac{3}{2}mgL \\
-\frac{3}{4}MgL
\end{bmatrix}
$$

代入$k_1=k, k_2 = 3k, M = 2mL$

$$
mL\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{7}{2} &amp; \frac{3}{2}L \\
\frac{3}{2}L &amp; \frac{45}{32}L^2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot{y} \\
\ddot{\theta}
\end{bmatrix}+ 
k\begin{bmatrix}
4 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; \frac{3}{4}L^2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
y \\
\theta
\end{bmatrix}= 
\begin{bmatrix}
-\frac{7}{2}mgL \\
-\frac{3}{2}mgL^2
\end{bmatrix}
$$

则特征多项式为

$$
\begin{align*}
\left| K - \lambda M \right| &amp;= \left| \begin{bmatrix}
4k - \frac{7}{2}\lambda mL &amp; -\frac{3}{2}\lambda mL^2 \\
-\frac{3}{2}\lambda mL^2 &amp; \frac{3}{4}kL^2 - \frac{45}{32}\lambda mL^3
\end{bmatrix} \right| \\
&amp;= \frac{171}{16}\lambda^2 m^2 L^4 - \frac{33}{4}\lambda kmL^3 + 3k^2L^2 \\
&amp;= 0
\end{align*}
$$

计算特征值为

$${\lambda _1} = \frac{8k}{19mL}, \quad {\lambda _2} = \frac{8k}{3mL}$$

所以

$${\omega _1} = 2\sqrt{\frac{2k}{19mL}}, \quad {\omega _2} = 2\sqrt{\frac{2k}{3mL}}$$

特征向量

$${u_1} = \alpha \begin{bmatrix} L \\ 4 \end{bmatrix}, \quad {u_2} = \beta \begin{bmatrix} -3L \\ 4 \end{bmatrix}$$"><p>写出矩阵形式</p><p></p><div class="MathJax" display="block" div.data-content:
写出矩阵形式

$$
\begin{bmatrix}
M + \frac{3}{2}mL & \frac{3}{4}ML \\
\frac{3}{4}ML & \frac{9L^2}{32}(mL + 2M)
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot{y} \\
\ddot{\theta}
\end{bmatrix}+
\begin{bmatrix}
k_1 + k_2 & \frac{1}{4}(k_2 - 3k_1)L \\
\frac{1}{4}(k_2 - 3k_1)L & \frac{1}{16}(9k_1 + k_2)L^2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
y \\
\theta
\end{bmatrix}=
\begin{bmatrix}
-Mg - \frac{3}{2}mgL \\
-\frac{3}{4}MgL
\end{bmatrix}
$$

代入$k_1=k, k_2 = 3k, M = 2mL$

$$
mL\begin{bmatrix}
\frac{7}{2} & \frac{3}{2}L \\
\frac{3}{2}L & \frac{45}{32}L^2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
\ddot{y} \\
\ddot{\theta}
\end{bmatrix}+
k\begin{bmatrix}
4 & 0 \\
0 & \frac{3}{4}L^2
\end{bmatrix}
\begin{bmatrix}
y \\
\theta
\end{bmatrix}=
\begin{bmatrix}
-\frac{7}{2}mgL \\
-\frac{3}{2}mgL^2
\end{bmatrix}
$$

则特征多项式为

$$
\begin{align*}
\left| K - \lambda M \right| &= \left| \begin{bmatrix}
4k - \frac{7}{2}\lambda mL & -\frac{3}{2}\lambda mL^2 \\
-\frac{3}{2}\lambda mL^2 & \frac{3}{4}kL^2 - \frac{45}{32}\lambda mL^3
\end{bmatrix} \right| \\
&= \frac{171}{16}\lambda^2 m^2 L^4 - \frac{33}{4}\lambda kmL^3 + 3k^2L^2 \\
&= 0
\end{align*}
$$

计算特征值为

$${\lambda _1} = \frac{8k}{19mL}, \quad {\lambda _2} = \frac{8k}{3mL}$$

所以

$${\omega _1} = 2\sqrt{\frac{2k}{19mL}}, \quad {\omega _2} = 2\sqrt{\frac{2k}{3mL}}$$

特征向量

$${u_1} = \alpha \begin{bmatrix} L \\ 4 \end{bmatrix}, \quad {u_2} = \beta \begin{bmatrix} -3L \\ 4 \end{bmatrix}$$
